Class ArrayList<T>

java.lang.Object
model.ArrayList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of elements stored in the array.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>
public class ArrayList<T> extends Object implements Iterable<T>
The ArrayList class represents a dynamic array that can grow or shrink in size.
